<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>新鲜的十二个有趣的笑话。来自俄罗斯的笑话。</title><link>https://www.anekdot.ru/</link><description>来自俄罗斯的轶事是最有趣的笑话，故事，格言和短语，诗歌，漫画和其他幽默。他们于1995年11月8日发布。由Dima Werner编译</description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 02 Mar 2025 21:00:00 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>03 Martha 2025的Anecdot＃1</title><link>https://www.anekdot.ru/release/anekdot/day/2025-03-03/#1511066</link><description>- 哦，你在看什么？&lt;br /&gt; - 性与大城市。&lt;br /&gt; - 所以是Zelensky与特朗普在白宫！&lt;br /&gt; - 我这么说。</description><pubDate>Sun, 02 Mar 2025 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.anekdot.ru/release/anekdot/day/2025-03-03/#1511066</guid></item><item><title>轶事＃2 for 03 Martha 2025</title><link>https://www.anekdot.ru/release/anekdot/day/2025-03-03/#1511067</link><description>“特朗普先生，您说，您期望乌克兰代表团的访问很大。”您的期望成真了吗？&lt;br /&gt; - 是的！我下令剥夺他们的晚餐。</description><pubDate>Sun, 02 Mar 2025 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.anekdot.ru/release/anekdot/day/2025-03-03/#1511067</guid></item><item><title>03 Martha 2025的Anecdot＃3</title><link>https://www.anekdot.ru/release/anekdot/day/2025-03-03/#1511068</link><description>您如何看待他的任期后几个月后，特朗普将英语重命名为美国人？</description><pubDate>Sun, 02 Mar 2025 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.anekdot.ru/release/anekdot/day/2025-03-03/#1511068</guid></item><item><title>轶事＃4 for 03 Martha 2025</title><link>https://www.anekdot.ru/release/anekdot/day/2025-03-03/#1511069</link><description>感觉！特朗普完全影响了电影学院！奥斯卡被授予了有关俄罗斯人的电影，这是一个安慰的奖项，而不是与乌克兰就俄罗斯条款达成协议。</description><pubDate>Sun, 02 Mar 2025 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.anekdot.ru/release/anekdot/day/2025-03-03/#1511069</guid></item><item><title>轶事＃5 for 03 Martha 2025</title><link>https://www.anekdot.ru/release/anekdot/day/2025-03-03/#1511070</link><description>当我和丈夫发誓时，我总是向我的朋友寻求建议。她对此一无所知 - 毕竟，她已经有三个丈夫。我听 - 完全相反。到目前为止，它的行为。</description><pubDate>Sun, 02 Mar 2025 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.anekdot.ru/release/anekdot/day/2025-03-03/#1511070</guid></item><item><title>anecdot＃6 for 03 Martha 2025</title><link>https://www.anekdot.ru/release/anekdot/day/2025-03-03/#1511071</link><description>做出什么决定都没关系。在什么条件下都没关系。我们仍然必须与您付款。</description><pubDate>Sun, 02 Mar 2025 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.anekdot.ru/release/anekdot/day/2025-03-03/#1511071</guid></item><item><title>轶事＃7 for 03 Martha 2025</title><link>https://www.anekdot.ru/release/anekdot/day/2025-03-03/#1511072</link><description>“你知道我们周围只有混蛋吗？”&lt;br /&gt; “我知道，混蛋。”</description><pubDate>Sun, 02 Mar 2025 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.anekdot.ru/release/anekdot/day/2025-03-03/#1511072</guid></item><item><title>03 Martha 2025的轶事＃8</title><link>https://www.anekdot.ru/release/anekdot/day/2025-03-03/#1511073</link><description>“如果您是处女，切勿与孩子谈论它。”</description><pubDate>Sun, 02 Mar 2025 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.anekdot.ru/release/anekdot/day/2025-03-03/#1511073</guid></item><item><title>轶事＃9 for 03 Martha 2025</title><link>https://www.anekdot.ru/release/anekdot/day/2025-03-03/#1511074</link><description>Lavrov称Zelensky为“纯纳粹”。他何时何地设法闻到他是未知的。</description><pubDate>Sun, 02 Mar 2025 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.anekdot.ru/release/anekdot/day/2025-03-03/#1511074</guid></item><item><title>轶事＃10 for 03 Martha 2025</title><link>https://www.anekdot.ru/release/anekdot/day/2025-03-03/#1511075</link><description>这个世界显然是由上帝在本季度末的夜班中创造的。</description><pubDate>Sun, 02 Mar 2025 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.anekdot.ru/release/anekdot/day/2025-03-03/#1511075</guid></item></channel></rss>